        },
        {
          "when": [
            {
              "kind": "flag_is",
              "flag": "flag.played_both",
              "equals": true
            }
          ],
          "setsFlags": [],
          "overrideDialogueId": "dialogue.kestrel_played"
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "id": "dialogue.kestrel",
      "format": "ink-json",
      "inkVersion": "21",
      "sourceHash": "1f46ef76393261",
      "compiled": {
        "inkVersion": 21,
        "root": [
          [
            "ev",
            true,
            "/ev",
            {
              "VAR=": "met_kestrel",
              "re": true
            },
            "^A woman in a sharkskin coat doesn't look up from her cigarette. \"Varga send you? No? Good — she's slow. I'm not.\"",
            "\n",
            "^\"I've got work that pays better than loyalty. Interested, or are you already one of hers?\"",
            "\n",
            "ev",
            "str",
            "^What's the job?",
            "/str",
            "/ev",
            {
              "*": "0.c-0",
              "flg": 20
            },
            "ev",
            "str",
            "^I'm nobody's.",
            "/str",
            "/ev",
            {
              "*": "0.c-1",
              "flg": 20
            },
            "ev",
            "str",
            "^I'm with Varga.",
            "/str",
            "/ev",
            {
              "*": "0.c-2",
              "flg": 20
            },
            {
              "c-0": [
                "\n",
                "^\"Intercept a courier before Varga's people do. Simple. Lucrative. Quiet.\"",
                "\n",
                "end",
                {
                  "->": "0.g-0"
                },
                {
                  "#f": 5
                }
              ],
              "c-1": [
                "\n",
                "^\"Smart. Stay that way and we'll get along fine.\"",
                "\n",
                "end",
                {
                  "->": "0.g-0"
                },
                {
                  "#f": 5
                }
              ],
              "c-2": [
                "\n",
                "^She finally looks up, unhurried. \"Pity. Tell her Kestrel says hello.\"",
                "\n",
                "end",
                {
                  "->": "0.g-0"
                },
                {
                  "#f": 5
                }
              ],
              "g-0": [
                "done",
                null
              ]
            }
          ],
          "done",
          {
            "global decl": [
              "ev",
              false,
              {
                "VAR=": "met_kestrel"
              },
              "/ev",
              "end",
              null
            ]
          }
        ],
        "listDefs": {}
      },
      "declaredVars": [
        "met_kestrel"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "dialogue.kestrel_sided",
      "format": "ink-json",
      "inkVersion": "21",
      "sourceHash": "047cecc9c7dd96",
      "compiled": {
        "inkVersion": 21,
        "root": [
          [
            "^Kestrel actually smiles when she sees you — brief, but real. \"My kind of mistake. Varga's still counting what you cost her.\" She tips two fingers off her brow. \"Stick around. The work only gets better from here.\"",
            "\n",
            "ev",
            "str",
            "^I'm listening.",
            "/str",
            "/ev",
            {
              "*": "0.c-0",
              "flg": 20
            },
            "ev",
            "str",
            "^Don't get comfortable.",
            "/str",
            "/ev",
            {
              "*": "0.c-1",
              "flg": 20
            },
            {
              "c-0": [
                "\n",
                "^\"Good. Patience pays, in this line.\"",
                "\n",
                "end",
                {
                  "->": "0.g-0"
                },
                {
                  "#f": 5
                }
              ],
              "c-1": [
                "\n",
                "^\"Wouldn't dream of it. That's your job, not mine.\"",
                "\n",
                "end",
                {
                  "->": "0.g-0"
                },
                {
                  "#f": 5
                }
              ],
              "g-0": [
                "done",
                null
              ]
            }
          ],
          "done",
          null
        ],
        "listDefs": {}
      },
      "declaredVars": []
    },
    {
      "id": "dialogue.kestrel_refused",
      "format": "ink-json",
      "inkVersion": "21",
      "sourceHash": "03568008e56db5",
      "compiled": {
        "inkVersion": 21,
        "root": [
          [
            "^She doesn't bother with the smile this time. \"Loyalty. Cute.\" A thin exhale of smoke. \"Expensive, too — you just haven't seen the bill yet. Varga always lets it run a while before she hands it over.\"",
            "\n",
            "ev",
            "str",
            "^Suits me.",
            "/str",
            "/ev",
            {
              "*": "0.c-0",
              "flg": 20
            },
            {
              "c-0": [
                "\n",
                "^\"It always does. Right up until it doesn't. Door's behind you.\"",
                "\n",
                "end",
                {
                  "->": "0.g-0"
                },
                {
                  "#f": 5
                }
              ],
              "g-0": [
                "done",
                null
              ]
            }
          ],
          "done",
          null
        ],
        "listDefs": {}
      },
      "declaredVars": []
    },
    {
      "id": "dialogue.kestrel_played",
      "format": "ink-json",
      "inkVersion": "21",
      "sourceHash": "17454e83bd8a0e",
      "compiled": {
        "inkVersion": 21,
        "root": [
          [
            "^She watches you over the rim of her glass for a beat too long. \"You worked us both. Varga and me, played off the middle.\" Something that isn't quite a smile. \"I'd be insulted if it weren't exactly what I'd have done. Just know I'm counting now — same as she is.\"",
            "\n",
            "ev",
            "str",
            "^That's the job.",
            "/str",
            "/ev",
            {
              "*": "0.c-0",
              "flg": 20
            },
            "ev",
            "str",
            "^Nothing personal.",
            "/str",
            "/ev",
            {
              "*": "0.c-1",
              "flg": 20
            },
            {
              "c-0": [
                "\n",
                "^\"It is. Right up until everyone's counting. Then it's just math.\"",
                "\n",
                "end",
                {
                  "->": "0.g-0"
                },
                {
                  "#f": 5
                }
              ],
              "c-1": [
                "\n",
                "^\"It never is. That's the part that costs you.\"",
                "\n",
                "end",
                {
                  "->": "0.g-0"
                },
                {
                  "#f": 5
                }
              ],
              "g-0": [
                "done",
                null
              ]
            }
          ],
          "done",
          null
        ],
        "listDefs": {}
      },
      "declaredVars": []
    }
  ],
  "quests": [
    {
