      "title": "Better Than Loyalty",
      "giverNpcId": "npc.kestrel",
      "summary": "Kestrel, a rival fixer, wants you to intercept a courier before Varga's people do. Whose side are you on — hers, your own, or Varga's?",
      "offerWhen": [
